high_descs: Turn around and walk to the microwave.
Remove the cup from the microwave.
Approach the fridge on your left.
Place the cup in the fridge, wait, and remove the cup.
Turn to your left and walk to the coffee maker.
Place the cup in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled cup in the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn to the left, go to the microwave.
Take the black coffee cup out of the microwave.
Turn to the right, walk to the fridge.
Put the coffee cup next to the tomato in the fridge for a few seconds, take the coffee cup out of the fridge.
Turn to the left, walk to the coffee maker.
Place the coffee cup on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled coffee cup on the coffee maker.

high_descs: turn to face microwave oven on counter top
open microwave oven door, pick up black mug from inside microwave, close the door
walk to the right to face the fridge
open the fridge door, place mug on shelf next to apple, close door, wait, open door, pick up mug, close door
turn around, walk through kitchen to coffee maker on the left, turn to face coffee maker
place mug inside coffee maker on counter top
anns.task_desc: put a chilled black mug in the coffee maker
